de.payleven.payment

Interface PaylevenRegistrationListener


  • public interface PaylevenRegistrationListener
    Reacts on the result of the payleven registration.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onError(PaylevenError error)
      Called in case of an error during the registration process.
      void onRegistered(Payleven payleven)
      If registration was successful, the object returned in the parameter can be used to start the payment process.

    • Method Detail

      • onRegistered

        void onRegistered(Payleven payleven)
        If registration was successful, the object returned in the parameter can be used to start the payment process. Payment process involves selecting the terminal and starting the payment task.
        Parameters:
        payleven - initialized object ready for making payments

      • onError

        void onError(PaylevenError error)
        Called in case of an error during the registration process.
        Parameters:
        error - may be one of the following
        NetworkError in case of no network or internet connection
        PaylevenError any other case. This is also a super class for other possible errors.
